    "description": {
      "zh": "这款神秘农场 (Mystery Ranch) 背包专为短期任务而打造，可容纳至多 2 天所需的装备给养。优秀的人机工效部分抵消了背包容量有限的缺点，附加绑带系统提供了额外的挂点，可方便地将任务途中所需的工具与装备加挂在背包上。",
      "en": "This Mystery Ranch backpack is designed for short missions of up to two days. Its compact size is offset by excellent ergonomics. External straps provide convenient attachment points for tools and gear you might need on the go."
